observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the concerned officers should faithfully comply
with the provision of COA Circular No. 2013-004 on the requirement to
submit the list of all on-going government projects/programs/
activities and those that are to be implemented during the year
containing the following information:
a) The project name;
b) Implementing unit, Office or division if it is not the agency
as a whole;
c) Brief description of the PPA;
d) Contractor or supplier, if any;
e) Mode of procurement;
f) Funding Source;
g) Cost of approve budget;
h) Project duration including start and completion date; and
i) Location
